%h1 Welcome

%h2
  Queue size:
  = @queued

%h2
  Pool size:
  = @pooled

%h2
  Schedule entries:
  = schedule.entries.size

- if schedule.entries.any?
  %ul
    - schedule.entries.each do |entry|
      %li
        %pre&= entry.inspect

%p
  You have reached the default welcome page for skeletra, a sinatra skeleton
  app. You can find this page in views/index.haml.

%p
  If CSS is working properly, this page should be black.

%p
  If javascript is working properly, you should see a message here:

#js-test-output

%ul
  %li
    %a{href: "/tick"} tick
  %li
    %a{href: "/ping"} ping
  %li
    %a{href: "/schedule/clear"} clear schedule
  %li
    %a{href: "/work/clear"} clear work
